"DATA COMMUNICATION NETWORK TOPOLOGIES “You need to implement the virtual "
"topology specified in the task using MPI capabilities for working with "
"communicators and topologies, and ensure the ability to transfer data "
"from any selected process to any other process. (Do not use "
"MPI_Cart_Create and MPI_Graph_Create)”"
